### Register a new patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "patientjohn",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "13456789",
  "pesel": null,
  "role": "PATIENT"
}

